               <provenance>According to Additio 2, the Ms. was donated
                     by Walda Yoḥannǝs. His name and the names of his family members are written in
                     the supplication formulas which appear throughout the Ms. They were added later
                     by a very poor hand, the same as that of Additio 2.</provenance></history>
